\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf3 McMillan disputed Hearne's version of events. McMillan testified that when he arrived at the theatre, he carried the extension ladder into the building and placed it on the floor near the area in which Hearne was standing. McMillan testified that he told Hearne "to hold on and that}
{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf3 \~[**4]\~}{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\loch\af2\dbch\af2
